These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, august, november, july, june, march
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Birthday   | august | june | september | march | july | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
City: paris, marseilles, prague, hamburg, berlin, hannover
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| City   | hamburg | paris | prague | hannover | berlin | marseilles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
6 different games are played: chess, go, mah-jongg, bridge, billiard, canasta
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing go is on the far left##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Game   | go | mah-jongg | billiard | chess | canasta | bridge |

