.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, tea, milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |     4     |   5    |    6    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk | iced-tea | juice | tea | lemonade |

