.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-19::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, fonseca, bongani, bluemaster, aristoff, dunhill
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |  3   |    4    |     5      |   6   |
| Cigar   | bongani | bluemaster | aristoff | dunhill | davidoff | fonseca |

