.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-20::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: fuchsia, apricot, lilac, ivory, coral, black
1. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes black##1
5. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4      |      5      |   6   |
| Color   | fuchsia | lilac | black | coral | apricot | ivory |

 